Class WiFiConnect

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse211.finalproject.display.WiFiConnect

  • public class WiFiConnect
extends java.lang.Object
    Uses WifiConnection to communicate with server and receive map data. This class allows the robot to get an idea of the map that the competition will take place in.
